{"url": "https://book.douban.com/subject/1000090/", "id": "1000090", "title": "韦伯学说", "cover": "https://img1.doubanio.com/view/subject/l/public/s1338338.jpg", "base": "作者:顾忠华出版社:广西师范大学出版社出版年:2004-07页数:232定价:19.60装帧:平装丛书: 思想史研究小丛书ISBN:9787563346714", "intro": "在人类知识领域的浩瀚星空中，马克斯·韦伯（MaxWeber）的学说持久闪耀着魅惑而迷人的思想光辉。虽然世易时移，但韦伯的思想始终在“现实性”的背景之下长期被关注，成为当代最重要的思想资源。本书是汉语学界最为准确、全面地理解阐释韦伯学说以及梳理韦伯学史之力作。作者澄清了韦伯研究中惯常的理论误区与思想盲点，还原了韦伯学说本有的奥妙和魅力。顾忠华，1956年生，德国海德堡大学社会学博士。现任台湾政治大学社会学研究所教授。", "tags": ["韦伯", "社会学", "马克斯·韦伯", "顾忠华", "经典解读", "社会理论", "广西师大", "韦伯研究"], "score": {"avg": " 7.7 ", "scroe_num": "94", "rating": ["12.8%", "55.3%", "30.9%", "1.1%", "0.0%"]}, "comments": [{"comment_id": "748263063", "nick_name": "悟仁", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/3742596/", "head_image": "https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u3742596-37.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "user-stars allstar30 rating", "comment_time": "2013-11-25", "content": "<span class=\"short\">以有涯随无涯，殆己。顾中华水平蛮高的，能把社会学拓宽到大历史小人物的视野。</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "446003295", "nick_name": "Jasper", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/jasper1923/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1645272-45.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "user-stars allstar30 rating", "comment_time": "2011-10-13", "content": "<span class=\"short\">主要看了韦伯与马克思的比较与差异那段</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "309189023", "nick_name": "veeltalige", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/catsupke/", "head_image": "https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u2200461-38.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "user-stars allstar30 rating", "comment_time": "2010-10-29", "content": "<span class=\"short\">明白人写的书</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "224666935", "nick_name": "俄狄浦斯", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/OedipusSHH/", "head_image": "https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u3081902-19.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "user-stars allstar30 rating", "comment_time": "2010-03-04", "content": "<span class=\"short\">还行，首尾两部分较好~</